      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Progressive filly SENSES (2) comes off a real eye-catcher in the NSW Oaks where she drifted back but hit the line hard for second. Has yet to miss the top-two and led to win at this circuit and distance three back so should be prominent from the low draw. Looks nicely placed dropping from Group 1 level. BETTORLEFTALONE (7) drew the outside barrier and worked so did well to box on for a 3.2m third last week. Won two in a row prior, coming from wider than this for an easy win at this circuit and distance two back. Threat if things go his way. NOCTURNAL (6) was first up since the NSW Derby when he beat a handy field to win last week at Bathurst. Came from a similar barrier to this for second in a Derby heat at this circuit and distance three back so he is capable. DEVIOUS MINDS (1) came from this barrier to place here last month and has won at Penrith since. Could be competitive.",
